    <body>
        <p>New Castle, Henry County, Kentucky, tailor. Virginia native. Married to Darcus Pearce. Father of James W. Pearce, Thomas J. Pearce, Amanda Pearce. Tailor in Henry County in 1860. </p>

    </body>
